    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(…) <emph>Preceptum scriptum</emph> ... per <persName ref="#people/4149"
                            key="#Writer #Clergy/religious_persons">Aceprandum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Clergy/religious_persons">levitam</rs> et <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scribam</rs> sacri palatii anno septimodecimo principatus ipsius domni
                        Gisulfi, mense septembri, indictione duodecima, quod ab utili anulo
                        consignatum est. Et continebat qualiter ipse domnus <persName
                            ref="#people/4105" key="#Princeps">Gisulfus</persName> confirmaverat in
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3729" key="#Mother_churches">Sancte Dei
                            genitricis semperque virginis Marie</orgName> ipsius <placeName
                            ref="#places/4771" key="#Cities #Landed_possessions">Pestani</placeName>
                        episcopatus, in qua ipse domnus <persName ref="#people/4121" key="#Bishops"
                            >Amatus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> preerat, integras ipsas <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs> quas parti suprascripti episcopii
                        pertinebant per suprascriptas primam et secundam et tertiam cartulas
                        scriptas per ipsum <persName ref="#people/4420" key="#Notary"
                            >Ademarium</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs>, cum omnibus que intra eas erant cunctisque
                        earum pertinentiis et cum vice de viis suis, ut semper essent in potestate
                        ipsius domni Amati episcopi et successorum eius et partium suprascripti
                        episcopii ad faciendum de eo quod vellent, sicut ipsum preceptum
                        continet.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
