                    here). <emph>Document summaries</emph>: Schipa 1887 [1968]*, n. 60, p. 764
                    [267]* (source of the text reproduced here).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p> Di Meo 1795-1819, VII, p. 398. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
